snippet.title: DEZAEMON  BSX VERSION - BS-X Shooting gameplay (Satellaview)
snippet.description:
EDIT: Dezaemon BS Ban - BS-X Shooting was put up for download on Satellablog on 11/04/2011:
http://superfamicom.org/blog/2011/11/new-rom-dumps-bs-x-shooting-extras/

This Dezaemon engine shmup is a short yet fun burst of comical BS-X action.


As opposed to the previous NND mirror, this was recorded off a modified ZSNES setup by myself.
